{
  "stem": "151.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And she said, 'Do you see this chimney?' I said, 'Yes.' She says, 'There go your parents and when you'll be reun-- when you go through the chimneys, you'll be reunited.'",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I turned to my fellow prisoners and I said, 'What is she talking about?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What does that mean?' I mean, even in my darkest nightmare I could not have imagined the things that were going on here.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But let me go back for a moment because you asked me about Mengele and when did I find out about Mengele.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we came-- when we were permitted to walk into the barrack from standing outside after the shower, one of my neighbors a young girl one of my neighbors, tapped me on the shoulders and pointed to this Nazi officer who was the same officer we met at the-- on the railroad station.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she said to me, 'He's asking for you.' And I looked over there and this officer was waving to me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, you must understand we were totally naked.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I still had my hair, my blonde hair.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I turned away pretending that I didn't notice, didn't see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this friend again said to me, 'You better go over there.'",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I will never forget.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know I come from a family where my father I don't think ever saw me in my slip, not naked.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And here I'm standing, how am I going to go over there?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I cross my arms.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't know where to hide myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I went over there, he was with another doctor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think his name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Klein.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
